WHO USES IT
L3 Colorists doing preliminary grading; L2 Engineers implementing Lumetri-
compatible DCTL transforms; DITs generating on-set looks.

WHAT PROBLEM IT SOLVES
Ensures that a Lumetri grade exported as a LUT or AMF can be faithfully
reproduced on another GIOP system. Defines the exact tone mapping formula
used by Lumetri, ending the inconsistency between Adobe and other platforms.

